{"id":376753,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/01/仕图｜广电总局指导后，所有范冰冰半身像都变了/","date":"2015-01-03T06:09:03Z","modified":"2015-09-18T01:14:48Z","title":"仕图｜广电总局指导后，所有范冰冰半身像都变了大头贴","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/01.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376754\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/01.jpeg\" alt=\"0\" width=\"450\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/01.jpeg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/01-300x203.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>范冰冰版本的武媚娘在被广电总局指导下修改之后，很多地方变得不太一样了。</p>\n<p>马伯庸贴了几张图，发现是许改原则如此:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6402.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376777\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6402.jpeg\" alt=\"640\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6402.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6402-300x165.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n修改之前的样子是这样的</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-12.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376755\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-12.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (1)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-12.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-12-300x170.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n通过放大画面的一部分更改景别，把一些禁忌的东西推到画面外面去。</p>\n<p>根据这样的规则分析，可能广电总局认为半身镜头不好，身份证式的大头贴镜头更符合中国国情。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-22.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376756\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-22.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (2)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-22.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-22-300x165.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a></p>\n<p>好吧，我们整体来看看过去的画面里哪个不符合。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-31.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376757\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-31.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (3)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-31.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-31-300x204.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n半身照，不符合。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-4.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376758\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-4.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (4)\" width=\"300\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-4.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-4-229x300.jpeg 229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><br />\n大头照，符合。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-5.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376759\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-5.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (5)\" width=\"300\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-5.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-5-255x300.jpeg 255w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><br />\n《毛主席去安源》<strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6403.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376778\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6403.jpeg\" alt=\"640\" width=\"300\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6403.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/6403-280x300.jpeg 280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><br />\n《毛主席去安源之广电总局版》<strong>√</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-6.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376760\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-6.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (6)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-6.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-6-300x225.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n《水浒传》剧照 <strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-7.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376761\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-7.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (7)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-7.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-7-300x215.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n《水浒传剧照广电总局版》<strong>√</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-8.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376762\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-8.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (8)\" width=\"400\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-8.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-8-215x300.jpeg 215w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><br />\n修改前和修改后。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-9.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376763\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-9.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (9)\" width=\"300\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-9.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-9-200x300.jpeg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n唐朝的电视剧果然都很三俗。《西游记》<strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-10.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376764\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-10.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (10)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-10.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-10-300x173.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n果然好多了。不再心神不宁了。<strong>√</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-111.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376765\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-111.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (11)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-111.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-111-300x227.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n半身照不好，要改大头贴 <strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-121.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376766\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-121.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (12)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-121.jpeg 359w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-121-300x114.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 359px) 100vw, 359px\" /></a><br />\n天灭半身党，退胸保平安。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-13.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376767\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-13.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (13)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-13.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-13-257x300.jpeg 257w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n挺起胸膛的时代已经变了。<strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-14.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376768\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-14.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (14)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-14.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-14-300x94.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n这就有了切格瓦拉一样的目光，发现没有，总局在艺术上还是高明的。<strong>√</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376769\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (15)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15-300x168.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n当然了，修改这种艺术上的精益求精一定会有损失的。<strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376769\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (15)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-15-300x168.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n他手到底在下面干什么导致了这么剧烈的发射，你国观众会困惑一点儿。<strong>√</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-17.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376771\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-17.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (17)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-17.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-17-300x184.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-17-80x48.jpeg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n有的剧情只留一堆脸，确实会有理解剧情的困难。<strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-110.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376781\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-110.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (1)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-110.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-110-300x35.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a><br />\n你要交代他们在做什么，就留下面部分。不用局限在大头贴。<strong>√</strong></p>\n<p>当然了，总局本身也应该身体力行，冲锋在前。</p>\n<p>这样的也是半身的。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-18.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376772\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-18.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (18)\" width=\"300\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-18.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-18-300x252.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>×<br />\n</strong><br />\n改改改</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-19.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376773\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-19.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (19)\" width=\"300\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-19.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-19-300x200.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>√</strong></p>\n<p>果然慈祥多了。</p>\n<p>啊，让我们团结在以广电总局为核心的正能量影视剧前，少一些不雅的半身照，多一些漂亮的大头贴吧。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-20.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376774\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-20.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (20)\" width=\"300\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-20.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-20-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-20-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-20-70x70.jpeg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>×</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-211.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376775\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-211.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (21)\" width=\"275\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-211.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-211-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-211-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-211-70x70.jpeg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 275px) 100vw, 275px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>√</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-221.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-376776\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-221.jpeg\" alt=\"640 (22)\" width=\"350\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-221.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/640-221-300x25.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/8.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-368426\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/8.jpg\" alt=\"仕图\" width=\"200\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/8.jpg 258w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/8-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 258px) 100vw, 258px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016,9203,13789],"tags":[28541,18705,13438,9254,20474,26586]}